    # game/areas/howlersdell2thais.rpy:1370
    old "“It’s... {i}not{/i} what I expected to hear from a guild’s delegate,” she chuckles. “I must admit, you’ve managed to baffle me. But still... Keeping our distance for so long may be dangerous. Today, we’re strong, but if there’s one thing that the war has taught us, it’s that no place is {i}too{/i} great to fall.” "
