    old "You explain how you reached it and what you saw. She rubs her hands cheerfully. “Judging by your tale, they aren’t bothered by their humble lives, and even less so by what we try to build here. Splendid! I don’t need more chaos in our land.” \n\nShe leans forward with a smile, resting her chin on her wrist. “Only the oldest of our forest speakers have ever been in that place. It’s remarkable that you’ve managed to find it.” "
