    # game/areas/howlersdell2thais.rpy:1972
    old "She struggles to hide her smile. “Who were they, exactly?” Your story is brief, and she admits she’s never heard of them. As she’s holding her buckle, her voice suddenly grows solemn. “I hope their families will find comfort in what you’ve learned.” "
