    # game/areas/howlersdell2thais.rpy:1985
    old "Your tale takes quite a few minutes - not only does {color=#f6d6bd}Thais{/color} have many questions, she finally asks {color=#f6d6bd}Eryx{/color} to bring her a wax tablet, in which she starts making notes. Once you’re done, she lets out a relieved sigh, and speaks more to herself than to you. “If it just so happens that the tribe will need {i}my{/i} help, I’ll be prepared to answer their call.” She looks you in the eyes and smiles warmly, then closes the tablet loudly. "
