    # game/areas/howlersdell2thais.rpy:1998
    old "“That old bat,” she grabs her deer-buckle, but you catch a glimpse of a smile in her eyes. “She must have convinced quite a few people to lie to me. I wonder what the caravans will have to say to that. Their {i}embarrassment{/i} will help our negotiations greatly.” "
