    # game/areas/howlersdell2thais.rpy:2013
    old "She looks away, with tightened lips. Her chest moves from deep breaths, and after a moment, she gestures for {color=#f6d6bd}Akakios{/color} to step closer. “Give [pcname] five rings,” she says without as much as looking at him. Her green eyes reveal a mixture of anger and amusement. “She’s in for a surprise,” she titters, making {color=#f6d6bd}the trader{/color} scuttle away once he leaves the coins on the table. “I was letting her do her thing for too long. I’ll get her next year.” "
